description: Demolition of existing building & erection of part three/part seven/part twenty storey block comprising 119 residential units (51x1, 58x2, 3x3, 7x4-bed) 445 sqm commercial florospace (use class A1/A2/A3/D1) 66 car parking spaces, alteration to existing vehicular access, children's play area & associated landscaping.
